{"tid":259691,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻屎貓開生日會，柒頭勿入。","createTime":"2017-05-27T06:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T05:17:07.000Z","uid":7049,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5ceb391e4084305de70f2e2f94ddd618f60ba2","tid":259691,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今晚，我唔去浦了。夜晚同臭搞生日會。 <br />\n我地book 了3樣野。第一樣 唔落咁多水既罐。 <br />\n<br />\n食一大罐吞拿魚雞肉罐，加少d水，約70幾克。 <br />\n<br />\n另一樣, 私伙的 生肉乾放題，約30克 ，<br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，脆少少，有咬口d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一個貓唔食得既生日蛋糕。 <br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多罐。 <br />\n<br />\n今晚 , 7點旺角地鐡站集合 <br />\n<br />\n貓女：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓仔：Model , 靚仔, 有鼻屎免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通貓仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧貓仔，識d俾得起$1000去生日會的貓女吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d生日會無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/145229_eaa25f3a43c0aaaaa39f8b04d9195a99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F145229_eaa25f3a43c0aaaaa39f8b04d9195a99.jpg&h=a52579ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/145252_3657afb7b8b8f11523cf7f855bb47e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F145252_3657afb7b8b8f11523cf7f855bb47e33.jpg&h=7b19e075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢終於一歲大啦，大家一齊黎參加生日會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0161add5459ab745be55e16cb5c1c6ea59e687c","tid":259691,"uid":19159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"中上樣 model樣 非厹 已切蛋不亂搞男女關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/152204_2041b0ce2c2de59fd